129	  it.todo("sword policy second claim of 1500 G with 600 G cap remaining yields payout 600 G and cap 0");
130	  it.todo("cursed sword: cap is 2000 G based on unmodified insurance value (premium modifiers do not raise cap)");
131	  it.todo("policy with sword + 3 runes: insurance sum 1750 G (block discount affects only premium, not insurance sum)");
132	
